headline: Bitcoin rally lifts Solana, Coinbase, and other crypto plays
summary: Bitcoin (BTC-USD) passes the $100,000 mark, raising the tide for other cryptocurrencies and crypto-related plays. Brad Smith and Madison Mills take a look at other names sharing in bitcoin's rise, like dogecoin (DOGE-USD), Ripple XRP (XRP-USD), Solana (SOL-USD), Tether (USDT-USD), and Coinbase (COIN). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Wealth here. This post was written by Naomi Buchanan.
